            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1441.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fish</strong> with the <strong>roast Tenderstem</strong> and <strong>rice</strong> to the side</p>\n<p>Tip: for fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p>\n<p>Spoon the<strong> teriyaki sauce</strong> over everything and garnish with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\n<p> </p>",
